        <article class="prog-event">
          <div class="prog-event-date">
            <span class="prog-event-day">2pm - 4pm</span>
            <span class="prog-event-num">Workshop with Rose</span>
            <span class="prog-event-time">1, 2, 3 Sleep!</span>
          </div>
          <div class="prog-event-body">
            <p class="prog-event-category">Come and discover an innovative system to improve your sleep!
Sleep is a vital need... but sometimes we just don't get it. Long nights without rest, restlessness, thoughts that go round and round... Sound familiar?
The Sounder Sleep System, created by Feldenkrais practitioner Mickel Grumdman, is a gentle yet powerful technique based on breathing and mini-movements.
A clear presentation of the system, a 30-minute guided practice, and a friendly chat over a Herbarius herbal tea!</p>
            <h3>Free</h3>
            <p>Saturday</p>
            <div class="prog-event-meta">
